FMCG Distribution & Sales Analytics | Power BI, SQL, Excel

Developed an end-to-end FMCG Sales & Distribution Analytics solution to monitor sales performance, distributor efficiency, inventory management, and delivery operations. Built interactive Power BI dashboards using a star schema data model and DAX measures to provide actionable business insights.

Key Features
Analyzed 20,000+ sales transactions across multiple distributors and products.
Designed a Star Schema data model for efficient reporting and analysis.
Created Executive, Sales, Distributor, Product, and Inventory dashboards.
Developed KPIs including Total Sales, Quantity Sold, Target Achievement %, Delivery Rate %, and Sales Growth.
Performed distributor performance analysis and product category evaluation.
Implemented Power Query transformations for data cleaning and preparation.
Created DAX measures for advanced business calculations and trend analysis.
Generated actionable insights to improve sales performance and operational efficiency.
Tools & Technologies
Power BI
SQL
Excel
DAX
Power Query
Data Modeling
Business Impact

The dashboard enables management to track sales performance, identify high-performing distributors, monitor delivery efficiency, optimize inventory levels, and make data-driven business decisions
